 competitive salary package.\r\n\r\n- Attractive annual performance bonuses and incentives.\r\n\r\n- Company-provided communication devices (laptop, mobile phone) and expense accounts for external meetings.',3,4000000.00,10000000.00,'NEGOTIABLE','PUBLISHED',NULL,NULL,'Monday - Friday 8h00 - 12h00 & 13h00- 17h00','trunghieu999909@gmail.com','0333180251','2025-12-06','2025-12-06','2025-11-14 02:56:51',44,41,41,'2025-11-14 02:56:37','2025-11-14 02:55:53','2025-11-14 02:56:51','2025-12-06');
